<p>I have a PF's selectOneRadio to choose a file type to download. Also I have a commandButton to call a download servlet using onclick attribute. The problem is that when I choose file type and click the button, the chosen value is of course not yet submitted. I'm looking for some way to get the chosen value available when I click on a download button.</p>  <p>Here's my code: </p>  <pre><code>&lt;p:selectOneRadio id="sorType" value="#{bean.type}" layout="custom"&gt;     &lt;f:selectItem itemLabel="XML" itemValue="XML" /&gt;     &lt;f:selectItem itemLabel="XLS" itemValue="XLS" /&gt;     &lt;f:selectItem itemLabel="CSV" itemValue="CSV" /&gt; &lt;/p:selectOneRadio&gt;  &lt;p:commandButton type="button" ajax="false" onclick="return downloadFile('#{bean.type}');" /&gt; </code></pre>